Legend has it that whoever holds the Power Core rules the world. In the fight to protect the Core, Quilin's mistake led to the extinction of his guild, then he was incarnated to a kung-fu rookie. After reincarnation, Qiulin found himself reborn with the ability of the Power Core to devour everything. With the help of the Core, Qiulin decided to regain the glorious moment of his guild!

(Source: Webcomics)

A child was abandoned in a forest infested with monsters and ghosts. Woon Sowol was adopted by the five masters and learned the best magical techniques. Although the five masters are godly beings, now their inner balance is on the verge of being broken down. Woon Sowol takes revenge on behalf of his masters, and goes to the world to become a god. In the end, will Sowol be able to get out of the forest of beasts?
(Source: KakaoPage, translated)
